{
  "levelId": "forest-04",
  "chapterId": "forest-04",
  "worldId": "forest",
  "title": "蘑菇谷：照顾小芽",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "mushroom",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/forest/forest-04.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "蘑菇谷里住着一颗害羞的小芽。它躲在大蘑菇后面，只露出两片叶子。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是蘑菇谷。我们先把“照顾小芽”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我闻到了叶子和雨水的味道，森林朋友就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先听树叶的声音，再用温柔的动作帮助这里的朋友。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "care",
          "prompt": "给小芽选择合适的照顾方式。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "放一片柔软树叶",
              "feedback": "小芽有了温暖的小被子。"
            },
            {
              "label": "唱一首轻轻的歌",
              "feedback": "小芽听着歌，慢慢探出头来。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，放一片柔软树叶让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "轻轻完成这一步，藏在叶影里的小路出现了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条小路和森林地图连起来，萤光就会为我们领路。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这片叶子的形状，下一次遇见它就知道该往哪里走。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "‘芽’虽然小，也值得被认真照顾。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
          "forest_guide",
          "hero"
        ],
